438
00:23:39.495 --> 00:23:40.795
What? Wait a minute.

439
00:23:42.395 --> 00:23:43.895
Heiji?

440
00:23:43.895 --> 00:23:45.595
I guess the time's not right yet.

441
00:23:49.795 --> 00:23:51.795
Well, at least I gave him back what I owed him.

